// Hunting query: anomalous Conditional Access policy block failures
//
// Tactic: Credential Access (TA0006) / Initial Access (TA0001)
// Technique: T1110 - Brute Force (supporting signal)
// Data source: Microsoft Sentinel (SigninLogs)

SigninLogs
| where ResultType == "53003" // Conditional Access Policy Block
| summarize FailedCount = count() by UserPrincipalName, IPAddress, Location, AppDisplayName
| where FailedCount > 5
| sort by FailedCount desc
